### Architecture Decision: **Hybrid — Backend Microservices + Lightweight Client Rendering**

| Concern | Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| G-code Generation | **Server-side** (containerized Python) | IP protection; CPU-bound; results cached in S3 |
| Nesting Algorithm | **Server-side** (containerized Python) | IP-critical MaxRects + proprietary scoring |
| 3D Visualization | **Client-side** (Three.js in browser) | GPU-accelerated; no IP exposure; low latency |
| G-code Parsing | **Client-side** (Web Worker) | Regex-only; not IP-sensitive; reduces server load |
| PDF Generation | **Server-side** (containerized Python) | ReportLab stays in Python; files served via S3 |

