### 5.4 Storage Strategy

| Data Type | Storage | Access Pattern |
|---|---|---|
| User data, projects, parts | **PostgreSQL** | CRUD, queries, joins |
| Machine profiles, tool libraries | **PostgreSQL** (JSONB) | User-scoped, low volume |
| Nesting results (placement coordinates) | **PostgreSQL** (JSONB) | Read on project load |
| Generated G-code files (.nc) | **S3 / Cloudflare R2** | Write once, download N times, expire after 30 days |
| Generated PDFs (labels, maps) | **S3 / Cloudflare R2** | Same as G-code |
| Uploaded Excel files | **S3 / Cloudflare R2** | Parse on upload, store for audit |
| Session cache, rate limits | **Redis** | High-frequency reads, TTL-based expiry |

