## 6. SaaS Infrastructure, Auth & Monetization

### 6.1 Authentication & Multi-Tenancy

**Recommendation: Supabase Auth** (built on GoTrue/PostgreSQL)

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Sign-up / Login** | Email/password + Google OAuth + Microsoft OAuth |
| **JWT Tokens** | Supabase issues JWTs; FastAPI validates with `python-jose` |
| **Multi-tenancy** | Organization model: users belong to orgs; Row-Level Security (RLS) in PostgreSQL |
| **RBAC** | 3 roles: `admin` (manage org, billing), `member` (full CAM access), `viewer` (read-only) |

```python
# FastAPI dependency for RBAC
async def require_role(role: str):
    async def checker(user: User = Depends(get_current_user)):
        if user.role not in ROLE_HIERARCHY[role]:
            raise HTTPException(403, "Insufficient permissions")
        return user
    return checker

@router.post("/generate")
async def generate_gcode(
    project_id: UUID,
    user: User = Depends(require_role("member")),
    billing: BillingService = Depends()
):
    await billing.check_quota(user, "gcode_generation")
    # ... queue generation job
```

### 6.2 Billing & Tier Architecture

**Payment Processor: Stripe** (better API, better docs, global coverage)

| Feature | Free | Pro ($49/mo) | Enterprise (Custom) |
|---|---|---|---|
| G-code generations | 5/day | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| Max parts per project | 20 | 500 | Unlimited |
| 3D Viewer | ✅ Basic (100K lines) | ✅ Full (10M+ lines) | ✅ Full |
| Machine profiles | 1 | 10 | Unlimited |
| PDF export | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Nesting strategies | Snake only | Snake + Spiral + Climb | All + custom |
| 2nd pocket (Shaker Step) | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Team members | 1 | 5 | Unlimited |
| API access | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ REST API |
| Support | Community | Email (24h) | Dedicated + SLA |
| File retention | 7 days | 90 days | 1 year |

**Stripe integration architecture:**

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Browser
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant S as Stripe

    U->>API: POST /billing/checkout (tier=pro)
    API->>S: Create Checkout Session
    S-->>API: Session URL
    API-->>U: Redirect to Stripe Checkout
    U->>S: Complete payment
    S->>API: Webhook: checkout.session.completed
    API->>API: Update subscription in DB
    API->>API: Unlock Pro features

    Note over S,API: Recurring billing handled by Stripe
    S->>API: Webhook: invoice.paid (monthly)
    API->>API: Extend subscription period
    S->>API: Webhook: customer.subscription.deleted
    API->>API: Downgrade to Free tier
```

### 6.3 Feature Gating Implementation

```python
# middleware/billing.py
TIER_LIMITS = {
    "free":       {"gcode_per_day": 5,  "max_parts": 20,  "strategies": ["Snake"]},
    "pro":        {"gcode_per_day": -1, "max_parts": 500, "strategies": ["Snake", "Spiral", "Climb (CCW)"]},
    "enterprise": {"gcode_per_day": -1, "max_parts": -1,  "strategies": ["Snake", "Spiral", "Climb (CCW)"]},
}

async def check_quota(user: User, action: str):
    limits = TIER_LIMITS[user.subscription.tier]
    if action == "gcode_generation":
        daily = limits["gcode_per_day"]
        if daily > 0:
            count = await get_daily_gen_count(user.id)
            if count >= daily:
                raise HTTPException(429, f"Daily limit reached ({daily}). Upgrade to Pro.")
```

