### 7.1 Cloud Provider: **AWS** (primary) or **Cloudflare Workers + R2** (budget alternative)

**AWS Stack (recommended for Enterprise path):**

| Service | Purpose | Est. Monthly Cost (MVP) |
|---|---|---|
| **ECS Fargate** | Run FastAPI + workers in containers | ~$50–100 |
| **RDS PostgreSQL** (db.t4g.micro) | Primary database | ~$15 |
| **ElastiCache Redis** (t4g.micro) | Queue + cache | ~$15 |
| **S3** | G-code, PDF, upload storage | ~$5 |
| **CloudFront** | CDN for frontend SPA + assets | ~$10 |
| **ALB** | Load balancer for API | ~$20 |
| **Route 53** | DNS | ~$1 |
| **ACM** | Free SSL certificates | $0 |
| **Total** | | **~$115–165/mo** |

**Budget Alternative (< 50 users):**

| Service | Purpose | Cost |
|---|---|---|
| **Railway.app** or **Fly.io** | FastAPI + workers | $20–40/mo |
| **Supabase** (free tier) | PostgreSQL + Auth + Realtime | $0–25/mo |
| **Cloudflare R2** | Object storage (no egress fees!) | ~$1/mo |
| **Vercel** | React frontend hosting | $0–20/mo |
| **Upstash Redis** | Serverless Redis | $0–10/mo |
| **Total** | | **~$20–95/mo** |

### 7.2 CI/CD Pipeline

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Developer"
        DEV[Git Push]
    end

    subgraph "GitHub Actions"
        LINT[Lint + Type Check]
        TEST[Unit Tests - pytest]
