> [!NOTE]
> **Next Steps:** After reviewing this blueprint, the recommended first action is to begin Phase 1, Week 1–2: extracting the core engine into a standalone Python library with comprehensive unit tests. This de-risks everything else and can be done in parallel with frontend design work.
